FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the type of the value in the custom fields section dictionary entry.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Status Change Date
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the date and time when the status of the ticket was last updated.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Status Change Reason
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the explanation or rationale for why the ticket's status was updated.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Type ID
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the id of the ticket type.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Type Name
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the name of the ticket type.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket External Identifier ID
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the id tag of the item part of the external system.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket External Identifier Type
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the type tag of the item part of the external system.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket External Identifier Owner
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the owner tag of the item part of the external system.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket ID
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the id of the ticket.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Name
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the name of the ticket

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Description
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains a brief summary or detailed information about the issue or request that the ticket represents. This description should be clear and concise to help with quick identification and resolution of the issue.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Type
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the guid of the task type dom instance.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Priority
FieldDescriptors.FieldType: Skyline.DataMiner.Net.GenericEnums.GenericEnum`1[[System.Int32, mscorlib, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089]], SLNetTypes, Version=1.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=9789b1eac4cb1b12
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the priority linked to the ticket. The priority can have on of the following values: Low, Medium, High & Critical.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Severity
FieldDescriptors.FieldType: Skyline.DataMiner.Net.GenericEnums.GenericEnum`1[[System.Int32, mscorlib, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089]], SLNetTypes, Version=1.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=9789b1eac4cb1b12
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the severity linked to the ticket. The severity can have on of the following values: Minor, Major & Critical.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Requested Resolution Date
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the desired or expected date by which the ticket should be resolved.

FieldDescriptors.Name: Ticket Expected Resolution Date
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Contains the date by which the resolution of the ticket is anticipated.
